\fs36 Herbs
\fs22 \
Herbs take the form of either a flower, grass, vine, stem, leaf, root, or seed.  Each herb has an amount that is defined by a use count.  Herbs are all edible and must be eaten to trigger whatever their effect is, whether beneficial or harmful.  Each Herb has effects that can be applied by eating them even before they are mixed in Alchemy.\
